SOFIA, Bulgaria â During visits to Sofia and Bucharest on Monday (11 September), EU Agriculture Commissioner Mariann Fischer Boel said the two countries have made progress in addressing problems in the agriculture sector, highlighted in Brussels' previous country reports. 
