In other news, Romania's media are reporting that anti-corruption prosecutors have launched an investigation into Army General Staff head General Eugen Badala and several other officials. 
At issue is a military supply deal in 2000 with the Tofan company. 
(Evenimentul Zilei, Nine o'clock - 12/09/06; BNR, Bulgarian Government website - 11/09/06)
